name: Does not create an account with the same data as an existing account
fullName: cypress/e2e/register-new-user.cy.js#User registration Does not create an account with the same data as an existing account

items.statusDetails:
`cy.request()` must be provided a fully qualified `url` - one that begins with `http`. By default `cy.request()` will use either the current window's origin or the `baseUrl` in `cypress.config.js`. Neither of those values were present.

https://on.cypress.io/request
